IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. RECORD-MOVE-NESTED-MATCHING-CHILDREN.

DATA DIVISION.
01 SOURCE-REC.
   05 CHILD.
      10 D PICTURE IS 999.
01 TARGET-REC.
   05 CHILD.
      10 D PICTURE IS 999.
      10 F PICTURE IS 999.

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
MOVE 777 TO D OF CHILD OF SOURCE-REC
MOVE 111 TO D OF CHILD OF TARGET-REC
MOVE 888 TO F OF CHILD OF TARGET-REC
MOVE SOURCE-REC TO TARGET-REC
STOP.
